videos.description: Kevin Durant says it was fun playing against Kobe Bryant one last time and that he was trying to send Kobe Bryant off right by "destroying" him every chance he got, in similar fashion to when Kobe faced Michael Jordan at the end of Jordan's career.
videos.headline: Durant: I was trying to destroy Kobe every chance I got
